// compiler/src/native_llvm_lowering.sfn
//
// LLVM IR lowering module. Converts textual `.sfn-asm` artifacts into
// LLVM IR for native code generation.
//
// This module orchestrates the lowering process by importing modular components
// from the ./llvm/ directory.

